- Watch catalog, GCash orders, sari-sari inventory, announcements

### v2.0 — Major rebuild
- AI Store Assistant (Anthropic API)
- Sales Statistics page
- Delivery Status Timeline (user-facing)
- Inventory images
- Left-floating toast notifications
- Order unique IDs (ORD-XXXXXXXX)

### v2.1 — UI restructure
- Left sidebar on admin dashboard, inventory, stats pages
- Profile dropdown in nav
- Gear icon for settings
- Settings tabbed (left-side nav)
- User dashboard: 3-column layout
- Order Management: sidebar filters + search

### v2.2 — Size & design
- Base font 18px, all elements scaled up
- Animated watch logo in nav bar
- Grandfather clock AI avatar (animated eyes, mustache hands, gears, pendulum)
- Form pages centered (max-width 680px)
